title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (20): Models of Dialog
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Chat-based Dialog
* Task-based Dialog

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-20-dialog.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/cWDt6GTOpLE
Next Video: https://youtu.be/yq5YuZ_QCxU

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
